# TODO using tmux,  nohup, or Systemd Service
1-Option 1: Using tmux
tmux is a terminal multiplexer that allows you to run multiple terminal sessions persistently.
2-Option 2: Using nohup
nohup runs commands without hanging up when the terminal closes.
3-Option 3: Using Systemd Service
Create a Systemd service to ensure the Streamlit app starts automatically on boot and runs in the background.
